Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 129th Weekly Dose of Optimism. So much=
 going on in the world right now: a flurry of executive orders and action c=
oming out of the White House, the AI industry (maybe) being turned on its h=
ead, and a nightmarish airplane accident occurring at an airport I am sure =
many of us have flown in-and-out of many times. The world can be a chaotic =
place, but it=E2=80=99s a good place.=20
